There are sources of information, for example, the journal Praktika Reklamy

19:13.000 --> 19:15.000
It is constantly published there

19:15.000 --> 19:19.000
The next point that can be taken into account is the comparison with competitors

19:19.000 --> 19:21.000
Look what competitors do

19:21.000 --> 19:24.000
We know how much advertising costs in the media

19:24.000 --> 19:26.000
How much it costs to hold a certain promotion

19:26.000 --> 19:28.000
How much it costs to promote

19:28.000 --> 19:30.000
How much it costs to make a video, etc.

19:30.000 --> 19:32.000
We know all these estimates

19:32.000 --> 19:36.000
Looking at what competitors do, you can safely calculate how much they spend

19:36.000 --> 19:39.000
And if you position yourself next to them

19:39.000 --> 19:42.000
You can determine such an amount or a little more

